<span id="freeTextContainer13463100627797635948">Well that was a great middle school novel about overcoming challenges and believing in yourself.<br/><br/>Ghost is an endearing character who is struggling to move past a traumatic event. Whilst people have particular perceptions of what kind of person he is, his own self worth and expectation that he will be let down are also a major theme in this book. I loved that he found a strong supportive role model in his coach and the determination of his mother to make her own success. I thoroughly recommend thi</span>
  <span id="freeText13463100627797635948" style="display:none">Well that was a great middle school novel about overcoming challenges and believing in yourself.<br /><br />Ghost is an endearing character who is struggling to move past a traumatic event. Whilst people have particular perceptions of what kind of person he is, his own self worth and expectation that he will be let down are also a major theme in this book. I loved that he found a strong supportive role model in his coach and the determination of his mother to make her own success. I thoroughly recommend this for NZ Y6-9.</span>
